sky.f1.uk.title: The Rise Of MVG (2013)
sky.f1.uk.description: Debuting in 2008 and bursting onto the scene in 2013 where he took the great Phil Taylor all the way, hear first-hand accounts of Michael Van Gerwen's incredible rise. Ep 5.

sky.f1.uk.title: Gary Anderson: Back2Back Champion
sky.f1.uk.description: Gary Anderson tells the story of his PDC World Darts Championship triumphs in 2015 and 2016, as the Scotsman become only the third player to win back-to-back titles. Ep 6.

sky.f1.uk.title: 30 Years of the PDC World Champs'
sky.f1.uk.description: In celebration of 30 years of the PDC World Darts Championship, take a look back at the very first tournament, a classic final from 2007 and one of the greatest legs ever played. Ep 1.

sky.f1.uk.title: The Greatest Final 07:Taylor v RVB
sky.f1.uk.description: In the final act at the Circus Tavern, two of the finest players to have ever played the sport created a match for the ages, as Phil Taylor and Raymond van Barneveld met in the final. Ep 3.

sky.f1.uk.title: Darts Gold: Taylor v Barneveld
sky.f1.uk.description: A chance to relive classic darts matches. Here is Phil Taylor against Raymond van Barneveld in the semi-finals of the 2013 PDC World Darts Championship at London's Alexandra Palace.

sky.f1.uk.title: World Darts Championship Final '21
sky.f1.uk.description: The curtain closes on darts' biggest event with the final of the 2021 PDC World Darts Championship at the Alexandra Palace. Here, Gerwyn Price and Gary Anderson go head to head.

sky.f1.uk.title: World Darts Championship Final '22
sky.f1.uk.description: Michael Smith and Peter Wright meet as the two standout players in the final of 2022 World Darts Championship. Will it be 'Bully Boy' or 'Snakebite' who wins the Sid Waddell Trophy?

sky.f1.uk.title: World Darts Championship Final '23
sky.f1.uk.description: Michael van Gerwen and Michael Smith clash in the final of the 2022/23 World Darts Championship at Alexandra Palace. MVG targets a fourth title, while Smith eyes his maiden win. (03.01)

sky.f1.uk.title: World Darts Championship Final '24
sky.f1.uk.description: The eyes of a nation were fixed on the Ally Pally stage as one of the great sporting stories, told by Luke Littler and Luke Humphries, concluded during the World Darts Championship final.

sky.f1.uk.title: World Darts Championship Final '25
sky.f1.uk.description: Luke Littler competes in a second consecutive World Darts Championship final, as the 17-year-old wonderkid takes on three-time champion Michael van Gerwen at Alexandra Palace. (03.01)

sky.f1.uk.title: Rob & Romesh Vs Darts
sky.f1.uk.description: With help from Luke Littler, Rob and Rom sharpen their own skills for a special challenge at this year's World Darts Championship. (S7, ep 4)

sky.f1.uk.title: WDC Final 2025: Littler v van Gerwen
sky.f1.uk.description: A recap of the final at the 2024-25 World Darts Championship from Alexandra Palace in London.

E4Plus1.uk.description: A Tummy Ache and a Whale of a Metaphor: Sheldon spends some days in hospital, but he's the world's worst patient and his behaviour takes a toll on everyone. (S2 Ep12/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Wreck of the Relationship: Homer and Bart take part in a father-son therapy exercise on a ship. While they're away, Marge gets involved in Homer's fantasy football league. (S26 Ep2/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Super Franchise Me: Marge opens a catering franchise after her sandwiches become a hit at the school. But then another franchise opens right across the street. (S26 Ep3/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Flaming Spittoon Acquisition: Stuart from the comic book shop invites Amy out on a date. Consumed by jealousy, Sheldon then asks her to be his girlfriend. (S5 Ep10)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Speckerman Recurrence: Leonard confronts the man who bullied him in high school, while Penny realises that she did her fair share of tormenting in the past. (S5 Ep11)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Shiny Trinket Maneuver: When Sheldon is dismissive of Amy's career, Penny, Raj and Leonard teach him that sometimes it's a good idea to pretend to care about things. (S5 Ep12)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Recombination Hypothesis: In the 100th episode of the US sitcom, Leonard and Penny agree to give their relationship another chance, but they soon start to argue again. (S5 Ep13)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Homer vs Dignity: Homer asks Mr Burns for a pay rise after the family have to dress up as a mariachi band and sing for their dinner. But Mr Burns has a better idea... (S12 Ep5/21)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Computer Wore Menace Shoes: After Homer publishes damaging rumours on 'Mr X's Web Page', he ends up on a Prisoner-style island, complete with guest star Patrick McGoohan. (S12 Ep6/21)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Hollyoaks
E4Plus1.uk.description: Darren extends an olive branch to Tony. Cleo receives some bittersweet news. And a resident opens up about recent abuse.

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: New Kids on the Blecch: After cheating in the Springfield Marathon, Bart is rescued from an angry mob by a record producer and is recruited for a new boy band. (S12 Ep14/21)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Great Celebrity Bake Off...
E4Plus1.uk.description: ...for Stand Up To Cancer: Greg James, Fern Brady, Spice Girl Mel B and Dermot O'Leary take on iced buns, a family classic and a celebrity doppelgnger in biscuit form.

E4Plus1.uk.title: Gogglebox
E4Plus1.uk.description: Great Expectations and Rise and Fall are on the box this time. And Wild Isles, Tempting Fortune, Married at First Sight Australia and Dance 100. (S21 Ep6)

E4Plus1.uk.title: New: Dating Naked UK
E4Plus1.uk.description: Brand new series - The Naked Newbie: Radical dating show presented by Rylan Clark. Heads are turned as a new naked arrival upsets the singletons' budding connections (S1 Ep2)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Naked Attraction
E4Plus1.uk.description: Zoe is struggling to find someone who shares her enthusiasm for the natural look. Derry is worried that his jet-set lifestyle is ruining his chances of finding love. (S4 Ep2)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Thanksgiving Decoupling: Howard takes the gang to his mother's house for Thanksgiving to protect himself from his grumpy father-in-law who has also been invited. (S7 Ep9)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Discovery Dissipation: Sheldon feels guilty when he gets attention for his accidental discovery of a new element. Raj stays with Howard and Bernadette for a week. (S7 Ep10)

E4Plus1.uk.title: First Dates
E4Plus1.uk.description: Dental nurse Jade hopes to get her teeth into a tall alpha male. She meets strapping, handsome tree surgeon Tom. And female sumo wrestler Sharran dates ex-bingo-caller David. (S10 Ep4) [SL]

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Lisa the Tree Hugger: A dramatic rooftop protest at Krusty Burger inspires Lisa to become an eco-radical - especially when she sees how cute one of the protestors is... (S12 Ep4/21)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Young Sheldon
E4Plus1.uk.description: A Race of Superhumans and a Letter to Alf: Sheldon agrees to help Missy with her maths homework. Georgie joins a bible study group to get closer to Veronica. (S2 Ep11/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Young Sheldon
E4Plus1.uk.description: A Tummy Ache and a Whale of a Metaphor: Sheldon spends some days in hospital, but he's the world's worst patient and his behaviour takes a toll on everyone. (S2 Ep12/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Modern Family
E4Plus1.uk.description: Can't Elope: Haley and Dylan's plan to quietly elope before the babies are born does not go as hoped. Jay tries to get his new business off the ground by courting an Insta celeb. (S10 Ep20)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Goldbergs
E4Plus1.uk.description: Livin' on a Prayer: Murray is feted by his old high school for his sporting prowess. Barry throws a party to impress his friends while his parents are away. (S1 Ep23)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Goldbergs
E4Plus1.uk.description: Love Is a Mix Tape: Adam tries to express his feelings for Dana by making her a mix tape, but disaster strikes when the tape falls into Beverly's hands. (S2 Ep1)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Neighborhood
E4Plus1.uk.description: Welcome to the Future: Calvin and Marty struggle to secure investment in their new business. Gemma's annoyed when Dave invites his boss to Grover's 13th birthday party. (S5 Ep18)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Neighborhood
E4Plus1.uk.description: Welcome to the New Do: When her usual stylist isn't available, Gemma decides to use Tina's hairdresser for an important work event. (S5 Ep19)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Thanksgiving Decoupling: Howard takes the gang to his mother's house for Thanksgiving to protect himself from his grumpy father-in-law who has also been invited. (S7 Ep9)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Hollyoaks
E4Plus1.uk.description: Theresa risks her own safety to help a spiralling Mercedes. And a resident worries about what a scorned ex is capable of...

E4Plus1.uk.title: Hollyoaks
E4Plus1.uk.description: Darren extends an olive branch to Tony. Cleo receives some bittersweet news. And a resident opens up about recent abuse.

E4Plus1.uk.title: Rude(ish) Tube Shorts
E4Plus1.uk.description: A short, cheeky clip from Rude Tube's naughty little sister Rude(ish) Tube, featuring sheep.

E4Plus1.uk.title: Ramsay's Kitchen Nightmares USA
E4Plus1.uk.description: Trobiano's: Gordon Ramsay meets struggling executive chef Anthony Trobiano, who's sinking under half a million dollars of debt at his restaurant in Great Neck, New York. (S2 Ep4) [SL]

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Goldbergs
E4Plus1.uk.description: Muscles Mirsky: When Beverly is caught out reading Erica's diary she promises to trust her daughter instead of snooping in future, but Erica takes advantage. (S1 Ep15)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Goldbergs
E4Plus1.uk.description: Goldbergs Never Say Die!: Adam and his friends go on a treasure hunt inspired by comedy adventure film The Goonies when Pops misplaces some family jewels. (S1 Ep16)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Replaceable You: When Homer loses his job to his eager new assistant, he teams up with Ned to reveal her evil past. (S23 Ep4/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Ten-Per-Cent Solution: The TV network cancel Krusty the Clown's show. Can his first agent, Annie (Joan Rivers), help him craft a comeback? (S23 Ep8/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Collaboration Fluctuation: Leonard, Penny and Raj settle into their new living arrangement, and Sheldon expresses an interest in Amy's professional life. (S10 Ep19)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Recollection Dissipation: Sheldon collaborates on two projects - one with Leonard and Howard, plus another with Amy - pushing himself to the limit. (S10 Ep20)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Modern Family
E4Plus1.uk.description: Crying Out Loud: Phil, Luke and Haley force Alex to come out and celebrate her senior ditch day, but they end up taking an unexpected detour. (S6 Ep23)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Modern Family
E4Plus1.uk.description: American Skyper: The whole family are at Jay and Gloria's for Alex's graduation party, except for Phil, who's figured out a way to be there using Skype and a robotic vessel. (S6 Ep24)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Prestidigitation Approximation: Leonard must choose between his new girlfriend Priya and his friendship with Penny. Howard drives Sheldon crazy with a magic trick. (S4 Ep18)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Zarnecki Incursion: When somebody hacks into Sheldon's online gaming account, he and his friends become determined to locate the culprit. (S4 Ep19)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Herb Garden Germination: Sheldon and Amy experiment on their friends by spreading gossip, while Howard takes a big step in his relationship with Bernadette. (S4 Ep20)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Agreement Dissection: Priya uses her legal expertise to dissect the roommate agreement and put Sheldon in his place, and the girls take Sheldon dancing. (S4 Ep21)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Young Sheldon
E4Plus1.uk.description: A Nuclear Reactor and a Boy Called Lovey: Sheldon attempts to build a nuclear reactor. Georgie is heartbroken when he learns that Veronica has a boyfriend. (S2 Ep13/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Young Sheldon
E4Plus1.uk.description: David, Goliath and a Yoo-Hoo from the Back: Sheldon uses his new friendship with the school bully to boss Georgie around. Missy steals Meemaw's make-up. (S2 Ep14/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Opposites A-Frack: Lisa calls on politician Maxine Lombard to stop Mr Burns' secret fracking operation but is taken aback when Lombard and Burns are attracted to each other. (S26 Ep5/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Simpsorama: In a crossover episode, the Simpsons meet the Planet Express crew from Futurama, who've travelled through time to present-day Springfield to stop a catastrophe. (S26 Ep6/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Beta Test Initiation: Leonard and Penny put their relationship through a 'beta test' and report problems with each other as 'bugs'. Sheldon and Amy seek internet fame. (S5 Ep14)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Friendship Contraction: After Sheldon keeps him awake all night, an irate Leonard decides he needs to break the roommate agreement, which formally ends their friendship. (S5 Ep15)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Vacation Solution: Sheldon helps Amy in her biology lab after he is forced to use up two weeks of holiday, but he is bored by the tasks that she gives him. (S5 Ep16)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Rothman Disintegration: Sheldon and Kripke argue over who should get Professor Rothman's vacant corner office. Amy buys Penny some art to celebrate their friendship. (S5 Ep17)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Great Money Caper: When Homer leaves Bart by the squid port, kind strangers start giving money to the 'street urchin'. So Homer and Bart turn to a life of scamming. (S12 Ep7/21)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Skinner's Sense of Snow: When a huge snowdrift engulfs the school, Bart leads the kids in a rebellion, gagging Principal Skinner and tying him to a chair as they run amok. (S12 Ep8/21)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Hollyoaks
E4Plus1.uk.description: All eyes are on Lucas as his desperate bid to win back Dillon begins to spiral out of control. Frankie confides in Dodger, but will his concern make her question her new beau?

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Simpsons Spin-Off Showcase: Troy McClure hosts a vision of the future of The Simpsons, in which Chief Wiggum becomes private detective Wiggum, P.I. (S8 Ep24/25)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Great Celebrity Bake Off...
E4Plus1.uk.description: ...for Stand Up To Cancer: Joe Locke, Rev Richard Coles, Adam Hills and Sara Cox take on biscuit bars and pastry and recreate their famous best friend in the Showstopper.

E4Plus1.uk.title: Gogglebox
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Goggleboxers watch The Great Celebrity Bake Off for Stand Up To Cancer, Race Across the World, Love Is Blind, The Dog Academy, Beef, Outlast and ITV News (Trump). (S21 Ep7)

E4Plus1.uk.title: New: Dating Naked UK
E4Plus1.uk.description: Brand new series - Dare or Bare: The first dumping has left the paradise markedly less idyllic. And a brutal truth-or-dare-type game ends in floods of tears. And squirty cream. (S1 Ep3)
